@universal_scheduler_be_HostAddress = http://localhost:5210
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Login (admin — set AdminSeed:Password in User Secrets)
# @name login
POST {{universal_scheduler_be_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@localhost",
  "password": "ChangeMe123!"
}

###

### Register (open — always assigns User role)
POST {{universal_scheduler_be_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

###

### Current user (requires bearer token from login)
GET {{universal_scheduler_be_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List dealerships (Admin only — requires dealerships:read)
GET {{universal_scheduler_be_HostAddress}}/api/dealerships
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get dealership by id
@dealershipId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
GET {{universal_scheduler_be_HostAddress}}/api/dealerships/{{dealershipId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create dealership (Admin only — requires dealerships:write)
POST {{universal_scheduler_be_HostAddress}}/api/dealerships
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Downtown Auto",
  "address": "123 Main St, Austin, TX 78701",
  "phone": "+1-512-555-0100",
  "timezone": "America/Chicago"
}

###

### Update dealership
PUT {{universal_scheduler_be_HostAddress}}/api/dealerships/{{dealershipId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Downtown Auto — Updated",
  "address": "456 Congress Ave, Austin, TX 78701",
  "phone": "+1-512-555-0199",
  "timezone": "America/Chicago"
}

###
